divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband saw a bright light and thought it was a satalite. An hour later it was still there. I took my camera and set it on a tripod and took two photos. He asked me to take photos of this light because he had never seen it there. Upon close inspection if the photo is zoomed it is not a star. It is an object with three dimensions which radiate black rays from the top and bottom and colored gold, orange and yellow rays from the side. The center is very white bright. If one looks at the upper right you will see the large face of what looks like an alien being (white face) it also looks skeletal.
